Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:18.61,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Ray Ray, bringing me back to life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.61,0:02:21.31,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}絆ほど強さ纏って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.31,0:02:24.76,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Wait Wait, what do you want from me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:27.84,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}この声を聞いたか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:31.44,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Ray Ray, bringing me back to life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.44,0:02:32.62,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}誇れるよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.62,0:02:34.37,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Drifting like a flawless ray
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:20.05,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}一次成形的世界线
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.05,0:01:22.42,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}已无法再倒带
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.00,0:01:26.42,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}被赋予的人生脚本
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.42,0:01:28.80,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}让其大放异彩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.89,0:01:46.05,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}感到些许迷茫  I leave it I leave it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.05,0:01:47.78,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}尽管看似玩世不恭
Comment: 0,0:01:47.78,0:01:49.44,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}only one heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.44,0:01:52.49,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}那并非徒劳  Don’t regret it regret it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.49,0:01:54.86,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}无论未来如何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.86,0:02:00.82,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}那本该唤醒的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.28,0:02:07.20,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}就算是飘渺的存在又何妨
Comment: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:08.42,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Don’t let go
